{"tid":477564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"西貢19歲仔全裸 離奇伏屍山坡","createTime":"2017-11-23T07:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T10:47:53.000Z","uid":9783,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e8363a767f920e9cd1e423c8ba0a090d95496e81","tid":477564,"uid":9783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:16:35.000Z","msg":"西貢青年赤裸離奇伏屍山坡草坪。下午1時許，一名年約19歲青年，被發現全身赤裸，倒臥在翠塘路1號對開山坡草坪，重傷昏迷，有途人發現慌忙報警。救護員接報趕至，經檢查後證實青年已經死亡。警方在場調查，懷疑青年從附近的建築物墮下，正追查死者身份及事件原因。"},{"pid":"9fe5b6f8de6323d28642e9be0899e2066898400b","tid":477564,"uid":9783,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:17:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171123/bkn-20171123141757893-1123_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171123%2Fbkn-20171123141757893-1123_00822_001.html&d=VT7FvYTkX2N6WbAcYSLOrDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=13f976ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171123/bkn-20171123141757893-1123_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3469e96034c93c48a15389a830b6a801a4b654bb","tid":477564,"uid":9783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:17:37.000Z","msg":"西貢特別多靈異野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f0a1de6c50aa53467976bb490bafe2d4c2ebf7","tid":477564,"uid":33095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:17:47.000Z","msg":"又一件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f14d35fe33a3df2436461e46ca786eae8c44b90","tid":477564,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:18:00.000Z","msg":"話說當年高登個柚木巴死左未"},{"pid":"d27524292e1c3e18fe2147004deafed76e4b7ec6","tid":477564,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:18:27.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocki